<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:qxa="true" id="_d98f8143-88df-4759-b935-f61cb6dfc27b" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>7.3.1</sptc><title id="_c5fe4541-8d1d-46d1-82a1-d8bc7c95843d">Application</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_872d0716-4f69-44c0-967c-617ad2846889" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2fed9085-300f-4a77-a151-4bc3751cb795">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4205_0.3.0.xml#_9fbc441b-1616-4781-bab4-59bee869a95f" id="_cb744f0d-3ec1-4f17-8698-0408894e0fbd" scope="local" type="part">Part 7.3</xref> applies subject to the limitations set out in <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/1810#_51ca7a80-a0a4-4bf6-8739-5c53b9741534" id="_04a2b7d5-758e-4d27-bb6a-1b3b2396209f" publishing-id="vol2" scope="external" type="subclause">H1D7</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_cad81394-c92a-4273-b879-89ed4d08d767" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_26f6b485-940e-46ac-88ee-1f5d35b224c8">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4205_0.3.0.xml#_9fbc441b-1616-4781-bab4-59bee869a95f" id="_2371a905-4362-4a55-b3ef-d80af968419c" scope="local" type="part">Part 7.3</xref> need not be complied with if <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/1810#_51ca7a80-a0a4-4bf6-8739-5c53b9741534" id="_d41dd45a-5816-45ee-aca1-94216c18f02c" publishing-id="vol2" scope="external" type="subclause">H1D7(3)(a)</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/1810#_51ca7a80-a0a4-4bf6-8739-5c53b9741534" id="_d7e9fcd7-9b43-4ecf-a398-ed4b993b2455" publishing-id="vol2" scope="external" type="subclause">(b)</xref> are complied with.</p></subclause><callout id="_26d0b0f1-016c-4376-8c7a-4344322bc392"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><title id="_cf133071-8020-4349-b0c0-9fab78c3dca9">Design wind speeds</title><p>Information on <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1242_0.16.0.xml#_84fc66d2-9804-4b12-8479-2240c139d62a" id="_1eb56407-f480-4462-8027-6c40b0bd0817" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">design wind speeds</xref> for particular areas may be available from the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1189_0.7.0.xml#_c1612e09-903f-47de-9ee0-00fb915ae751" id="_f3bd85d7-3bc8-49c5-8ade-9124e66530db" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">appropriate authority</xref>. Also see the table associated with the definition of ‘<xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1242_0.16.0.xml#_84fc66d2-9804-4b12-8479-2240c139d62a" id="_8014d892-d748-4a28-a797-10b0430f8c2b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">design wind speed</xref>’ for wind classes. A map indicating wind regions of Australia is contained in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4175_0.3.0.xml#_d5f40407-35b4-474d-8d94-5ff1fe7ed899" id="_022dd82d-94c5-4c18-9aea-6c55b58fb9b3" scope="local" type="part">Part 2.2</xref>.</p></callout><callout id="_fb467d1c-c4e6-43a4-a977-0e0181d80c57"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><title id="_c1bcc3c2-6e68-47ef-b813-1d80e82375a8">Other relevant roof tile requirements</title><p>In addition to the requirements of this Part, requirements for roof tiles also exist in NCC Volume Two and other Parts of the ABCB Housing Provisions. They include the following:</p><ul outputclass="alpha"><li>For the sizing and fixing of roof battens - NCC Volume Two <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/1808#_2d79fbfb-7cf2-472f-ac53-8b100c9faabd" id="_fd260fd4-0cd9-4f2c-b4c8-3a98e85e44f0" publishing-id="vol2" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">H1D6(3)</xref> (steel battens) and <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/1808#_ce1f1e96-c16e-4d79-afbd-ae4e90289707" id="_1ccf8a41-1745-450c-a9b6-d0487b209ea2" publishing-id="vol2" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">H1D6(4)</xref> (timber battens).</li><li>For sheet roofing over a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1455_0.7.0.xml#_c162af82-2477-499d-bdb1-39be88ffa668" id="_a6260483-4409-4bad-8073-e3786a97d344" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">separating wall</xref> - ABCB Housing Provisions <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4213_0.3.0.xml#_1a479cbb-10dd-4b3f-bd31-b0e665902ed1" id="_ebd92377-799e-4653-aea9-f27f559d2988" scope="local" type="part">Part 9.3</xref>.</li><li>For gutters and downpipes - ABCB Housing Provisions <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4206_0.8.0.xml#_1c715f7d-5c3a-432b-a4e6-08c8b0d54b10" id="_9b5cedfa-c31b-4b76-bcb3-50734aa5e616" scope="local" type="part">Part 7.4</xref>.</li></ul></callout></clause>